was introduced by Yingzi.

47
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:09,230
It's kind of like what that stupid woman did.

48
00:03:09,230 --> 00:03:11,710
Yes, she is so stupid.

49
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,920
Does she come from a wealthy family?

50
00:03:15,610 --> 00:03:16,890
Not really.

51
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:19,990
I went there with Yingzi once.

52
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:20,930
It's just

53
