Her father is a teacher in college.

55
00:03:25,790 --> 00:03:26,950
He's stupid, too.

56
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:30,110
My brother-in-law's family had hurt Yingzi so badly.

57
00:03:30,110 --> 00:03:31,550
Still, they taught their daughter

58
00:03:31,550 --> 00:03:33,829
to treat his family well.

59
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:34,930
I see.

60
00:03:35,510 --> 00:03:37,640
An apple never falls far from the tree.

61
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,640
Since she doesn't have much money,

62
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:42,329
why does she want to give up

63
00:03:42,329 --> 00:03:43,500
such a big house?

64
00:03:45,390 --> 00:03:46,220
Which one?

65
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,440
The one that will be auctioned soon.

66
00:03:53,050 --> 00:03:55,770
Shuo, why do you keep asking about Yingzi?

67
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,150
Do you like her?

68
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,110
I don't like stupid women.

69
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:02,620
I like smart girls.

70
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:04,350
Yes.

71
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:06,390
Yingzi is so stupid.

72
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:07,390
If others don't help her,

73
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:08,670
she won't survive.

74
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:11,820
I used to be the one who helped her.

75
00:04:12,590 --> 00:04:14,930
But now I've been working out.

76
00:04:16,110 --> 00:04:16,829
Shuo,

77
00:04:17,589 --> 00:04:20,589
Yingzi was really screwed over by my brother-in-law.

78
00:04:21,029 --> 00:04:22,490
Why don't you do her a favor

79
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:24,910
and keep the house for her?

80
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:25,550
Me?

81
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:27,590
I don't have time for that.

82
00:04:27,590 --> 00:04:29,610
Actually, I just think that house is nice.

83
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:32,000
I'm the plaintiff's lawyer now.

84
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,550
I know the ace in the hole.

85
00:04:33,570 --> 00:04:35,040
If she can't keep it,

86
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:37,100
I'll find a way to get it.

87
00:04:38,909 --> 00:04:39,390
I see.

88
00:04:41,659 --> 00:04:42,610
Okay, got it.

89
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:43,800
Go back to work.

90
00:04:46,110 --> 00:04:47,040
Have some water.

91
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,950
How stupid she is.

92
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:07,750
[Jingbei Court]

93
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:26,250
Let's meet them directly.

94
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,930
Let's go. Time is running out.

95
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:30,750
Look at your expression.

96
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:32,710
Yours is not any better.

97
00:05:33,690 --> 00:05:35,970
A man's life was lost because of one word.

98
00:05:36,570 --> 00:05:38,570
We have to exonerate the assailant.

99
00:05:39,409 --> 00:05:41,230
First, he may not be the one who hit him.

100
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:41,590
Second,

101
00:05:41,590 --> 00:05:42,350
protecting the victim

102
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:44,110
is the responsibility of the prosecutor and his lawyer,

103
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:44,909
not ours.

104
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,270
We have to protect

105
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:48,170
our client's legal rights.

106
00:05:55,909 --> 00:05:57,040
A plea of not guilty?

107
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:59,100
Yes.

108
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:00,700
Xu Jianshe.

109
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:03,110
If there is no new evidence,

110
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:05,470
it will be too risky to carry out the advocacy of innocence.

111
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:06,790
If it gets rejected,

112
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,780
you won't have any chance.

113
00:06:09,330 --> 00:06:11,270
You'll get a life sentence in the end.

114
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,710
For your benefit,

115
00:06:13,230 --> 00:06:15,160
we're going to do this in two steps.

116
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:16,110
Firstly,

117
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,510
Ms. Qiu will plead you not guilty.

118
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:19,590
Secondly,

119
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:21,350
I'll give you a misdemeanor defense.

120
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:22,280
In other words,

121
00:06:22,710 --> 00:06:24,350
who hit him

122
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,790
with those last fatal blows?

123
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:27,350
According to the current evidence,

124
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:29,100
it can't be accurately identified.

125
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,390
The criterion for the sentence of the first instance is too heavy.

126
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,050
In this way,

127
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:32,030
we are left a chance

128
00:06:32,030 --> 00:06:33,790
for a remand for retrial in the second instance.

129
00:06:33,790 --> 00:06:35,990
If the advocacy of innocence is rejected again,

130
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,909
you'll pay too much for the result.

131
00:06:37,909 --> 00:06:38,370
What do you think of it?

132
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:39,460
No way!

133
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,510
If you don't defend me as innocent,

134
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:50,050
I won't entrust you as my lawyers.

135
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:52,310
I didn't kill anyone.

136
00:06:52,909 --> 00:06:54,320
I didn't fight either.

137
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:55,950
I was there to stop the fight.

138
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:58,140
I have nothing to do with Li Zhanjun's death.

139
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:59,780
Do you understand?

140
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:02,830
It's fine that they didn't appreciate it.

141
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:05,030
But they even wanted me to plead guilty?

142
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:05,910
No way!

143
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,000
I won't compensate them!

144
00:07:08,110 --> 00:07:09,790
Mr Xu, please calm down.

145
00:07:09,790 --> 00:07:11,030
Calm down, okay?

146
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,990
You insist on the defense of innocence.

147
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:15,670
If it's not accepted by the court of the second instance,

148
00:07:15,670 --> 00:07:16,910
you'll lose completely.

149
00:07:16,910 --> 00:07:18,370
Think about it carefully.

150
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,120
Then I plead not guilty either!

151
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:22,160
Never!

152
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:25,210
You must plead me not guilty.

153
00:07:26,030 --> 00:07:27,890
Otherwise, I'll change lawyers.

154
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:33,270
Xu Jianshe.

155
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,100
This is the photo of Li Zhanjun

156
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:39,340
