157
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:41,590
Look at his injuries.

158
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:43,790
Do they have anything to do with you?

159
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:51,360
I won't look at it.

160
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:54,820
Don't play psychological warfare with me.

161
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:57,760
His death has nothing to do with me.

162
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,080
Why should I look at it?

163
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:31,560
Who is it?

164
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:37,470
Who?

165
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,620
Me, Yingzi.

166
00:08:39,990 --> 00:08:42,090
Why are you holding scissors?

167
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,380
You scared me, Lanlan.

168
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,670
You haven't been back for days.

169
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:48,590
And I'm watching the photos of a murder.

170
00:08:49,410 --> 00:08:51,830
How is your work

171
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:53,070
at Chen Shuo's law firm?

172
00:08:53,070 --> 00:08:54,070
Not bad.

173
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,630
But he is too stingy.

174
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:57,680
He only pays me 5,000 yuan a month.

175
00:08:59,830 --> 00:09:02,290
You can't chop off the flesh on a flea's legs.

176
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,020
Yingzi,

177
00:09:03,310 --> 00:09:04,790
I'm here to inform you.

178
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,430
Of what?

179
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:06,990
Sit down.

180
00:09:08,230 --> 00:09:09,070
Mr. Chen

181
00:09:09,470 --> 00:09:10,510
likes your house.

182
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:12,710
He kept asking me about your house.

183
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:13,990
He's been asking around a lot.

184
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:15,300
I asked him why he wanted to know.

185
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,830
He said he liked that house.

186
00:09:16,970 --> 00:09:18,170
If you can't keep it,

187
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,230
he'll buy it at the auction.

188
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,190
Just buy it.

189
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:23,630
Lanlan,

190
00:09:24,470 --> 00:09:26,200
tell him when you see him at work

191
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,930
that before I moved out of that house,

192
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:31,630
I had cast a spell on it.

193
00:09:32,310 --> 00:09:33,480
Besides me,

194
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:34,590
whoever moves in

195
00:09:35,310 --> 00:09:36,770
will die a horrible death.

196
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:37,630
Fine.

197
00:09:39,170 --> 00:09:42,890
[Da Zheng Law Firm]

198
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:42,310
That's what she said?

199
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,150
Yes.

200
00:09:43,190 --> 00:09:44,990
She looked so scary when she said it.

201
00:09:44,990 --> 00:09:45,990
It seemed

202
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:47,590
she hated you very much.

203
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:50,160
Shuo, I think you'd better forget it.

204
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:51,470
Just tell her

205
00:09:51,470 --> 00:09:52,870
I'm not afraid of ghosts.

206
00:09:53,090 --> 00:09:54,190
If this house isn't haunted,

207
00:09:54,190 --> 00:09:55,190
I won't buy it.

208
00:09:58,630 --> 00:09:59,510
Yan Qi.

209
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,880
You miss me?

210
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,470
I miss you too.

211
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,470
Let's have dinner together.

212
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,440
Okay, I'll call you later.

213
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,740
Zhang Shilan, book a table for me.

214
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,410
Mr. Chen!

215
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,240
You're a man of honor.

216
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,800
Ignore those bitchy women in society.

217
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,080
Which one is a bitch?

218
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:24,990
The one who came that day.

219
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:25,600
She doesn't look like a...

220
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,900
It's none of your business.

221
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:29,900
Don't ask questions that are not related to you, okay?

222
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,790
I'm just concerned about you.

223
00:10:32,810 --> 00:10:33,710
I don't need your concern.

224
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:35,320
It's not your job.

225
00:10:37,430 --> 00:10:38,470
I just think...

226
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,520
Shuo,

227
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,310
if you want someone

228
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:42,730
to be with you after work,

229
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:45,650
I can be the one.

230
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:49,050
You don't need to pay me extra money.

231
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,310
Okay.

232
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:54,470
Okay.

233
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,130
Get back to work.

234
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:15,990
Hello, Unscrupulous Cheng.

235
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:17,830
Don't bother me, okay?

236
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:19,990
You just want my house.

237
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:21,820
Take it if you dare.

238
00:11:23,110 --> 00:11:24,990
Let me kindly remind you again.

239
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:27,770
The deadline for the appeal is three days away.

240
00:11:27,770 --> 00:11:29,510
Don't worry about me.

241
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:30,570
Anything else?

242
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:32,320
I'll hang up if there's nothing else.

243
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,180
Righteous Luo.

244
00:11:33,410 --> 00:11:34,850
You introduced Zhang Shilan

245
00:11:34,850 --> 00:11:36,570
to me as an assistant.

246
00:11:37,110 --> 00:11:39,190
Are you up to something?

247
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:41,830
What are you talking about?

248
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,760
What could I possibly have in mind?

249
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,160
You think I'm not picky,

250
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:48,440
so you found someone to seduce me, right?

251
00:11:49,530 --> 00:11:50,930
What?

252
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:52,650
Unscrupulous Chen, what are you thinking about?

253
00:11:52,650 --> 00:11:54,480
I can take you to the hospital

254
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,740
to see if you have a delusional disorder.

255
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,620
Really?

256
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:00,880
It's not a honey trap?

257
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:03,870
Do you still need a honey trap?

258
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,750
Buddy, aren't you hunting everywhere?

259
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:07,480
I warn you, Unscrupulous Chen.

260
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:08,920
Don't bully Lanlan.

261
00:12:08,950 --> 00:12:10,410
Or I'll teach you a lesson.

262
00:12:10,430 --> 00:12:10,960
Bye.

263
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,150
What's wrong?

264
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:18,510
He said he thought

265
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,260
Lanlan seduced him.

266
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,900
I told you before.

267
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:23,380
You're playing with fire.

268
00:12:28,430 --> 00:12:29,110
Xue,

269
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,800
I thought Luo Yingzi

270
00:12:32,830 --> 00:12:34,900
introduced Zhang Shilan as an assistant

271
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,300
to get rid of this burden.

272
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,550
But I'm a little confused now.

273
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:40,320
She knows my nature.

274
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:42,950
Isn't she sending the sheep to the tiger's den?

275
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:45,740
You're doomed.

276
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:47,780
What?

277
00:12:48,830 --> 00:12:49,700
You're doomed.

278
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,060
I think

279
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,650
she doesn't like you at all.

280
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:55,950
What are you talking about?

281
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:57,250
I don't like her either.

282
00:12:57,250 --> 00:12:59,050
You know yourself very well.

283
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:02,320
Who did you fall in love with before?

284
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:04,830
You dug a hole

285
00:13:05,230 --> 00:13:06,340
and jumped inside.

286
